title: FELA: A Multi-Agent Evolutionary System for Feature Engineering of Industrial Event Log Data
summary: Event log data, recording fine-grained user actions and system events, represent one of the most valuable assets for modern digital services. However, the complexity and heterogeneity of industrial event logs--characterized by large scale, high dimensionality, diverse data types, and intricate temporal or relational structures--make feature engineering extremely challenging.
